题目内容: （1）求解以下方程组：$\begin{align}
  & \left     \{ \begin{align}
  & \frac     {3x}{4}+\frac     {4y}{5}=2 \\ 
 & \frac     {x}{5}=\frac     {y}{3}+2 \\ 
\end{align} \right     . \\ 
 &  \\ 
\end{align}$；（2）解一下不等式组：$\left     \{ \begin{align}
  & -4(x-1)\geq 5-x \\ 
 & \frac     {x+2}{4}-\frac     {1}{8}＞\frac     {x-2}{3} \\ 
\end{align} \right     .$．
